#. Used as HTML title of the page
#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:7
msgid "Open Innovation: Vital to Internet Health"
msgstr "Arloesi Agored: Yn Hanfodol ar gyfer Iechyd y Rhyngrwyd"

#. Used as HTML description of the page
#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:12
msgid ""
"Open Innovation means innovating collectively through shared ideas and open "
"source code."
msgstr ""
"Mae Arloesi Agored yn golygu arloesi gyda'n gilydd drwy rannu syniadau a "
"chod cod agored."

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:16
msgid "Privacy &amp; Security"
msgstr "Preifatrwydd a Diogelwch"

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:20
msgid "Digital Inclusion"
msgstr "Cynhwysiad Digidol"

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:24
msgid "Open Innovation"
msgstr "Arloesi Agored"

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:28
msgid "A healthy Internet is open for innovation"
msgstr "Mae Rhyngrwyd iach yn agored ar gyfer arloesedd"

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:32
msgid ""
"The Internet was built on the promise that any one of us might create the "
"next big thing. But in order to keep creating, imagining, and reinventing "
"our future online, the building blocks of the Web must be open to all. And "
"together, we need to make sure the policies and laws that govern those "
"building blocks are fair and functional."
msgstr ""
"Cafodd y Rhyngrwyd ei adeiladu ar y sail y gall unrhyw un ohonom greu'r peth "
"mawr nesaf. Ond er mwyn parhau i greu, dychmygu ac ail-greu ein dyfodol ar-"
"lein, rhaid i flociau adeiladu'r We fod ar agor i bawb. A gyda'n gilydd, "
"mae'n rhaid i ni wneud yn siŵr fod y polisïau a'r deddfau sy'n rheoli'r "
"blociau hyn yn deg ac yn gweithio."

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:36
msgid "A healthy Internet is created by you."
msgstr "‌Mae Rhyngrwyd iach wedi ei greu gennych chi."

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:40
msgid "Here are three areas where we can make a difference."
msgstr "Dyma dri maes lle gallwn ni wneud gwahaniaeth."

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:44
msgid "Support Open Source"
msgstr "Cefnogi Cod Agored"

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:48
msgid "Engage in Copyright Reform"
msgstr "Ymwneud a Diwygio Hawlfraint"

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:52
msgid "Influence Patent Policy"
msgstr "Dylanwadu Polisi Patent"

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:56
msgid "Open Source: Keeping the building blocks of the Web open for creativity"
msgstr "Cod Agored: Cadw blociau adeiladu'r We'n agored ar gyfer creadigrwydd"

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:60
msgid ""
"Open source should continue to be the heart of the Internet, so we can all "
"see, verify, and contribute to its future."
msgstr ""
"Dylai cod agored fod wrth galon y Rhyngrwyd, fel bod modd i ni gyd weld, "
"dilysu a chyfrannu i'w ddyfodol."

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:64
msgid ""
"Open source software – technology built with code that is open for view, "
"use, and modification – is the engine that powers a huge amount of the "
"Internet, from servers to operating systems to the bots that fetch your "
"search results. It’s the infrastructure that makes the Web a truly public "
"resource: transparent, trustworthy, and collaborative, so that anyone with "
"an idea can contribute. But much like our IRL infrastructure, we have to "
"commit the attention and resources to maintain it."
msgstr ""
"Meddalwedd cod agored – technoleg wedi ei adeiladu ar god sy'n agored i'w "
"weld, ei ddefnyddio a'i newid – yw'r peiriant sy'n gyrru cyfran fawr iawn "
"o'r Rhyngrwyd, o weinyddion hyd systemau gweithredu i'r botiaid sy'n estyn "
"eich canlyniadau chwilio. Hwn yw'r seilwaith sy'n gwneud y We yn wir adnodd "
"cyhoeddus: tryloyw, dibynadwy a chydweithredol, fel bo modd i unrhyw un sydd "
"â syniad gyfrannu. Ond fel sy'n debyg i'n strwythur IRL rhaid rhoi'r sylw "
"a'r adnoddau i'w gynnal."

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:68
msgid ""
"GitHub, the world’s largest open source community, includes 19 million "
"developers, 100,000 teams, and 52 million repositories for established and "
"developing technologies."
msgstr ""
"GitHub, y gymuned cod agored mwyaf yn y byd, sy'n cynnwys 19 miliwn o "
"ddatblygwyr, 100,000 o dimau a 52 miliwn o storfeydd ar gyfer technolegau "
"sefydlog a rhai sy'n datblygu."

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:72
msgid "Source: <a href=\"%(github)s\">GitHub</a>"
msgstr "Ffynhonnell: <a href=\"%(github)s\">GitHub</a>"

#. This is used as a decorative element in a callout box. Keep it short.
#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:77
msgid "52M"
msgstr "52M"

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:81
msgid "How you can support open source"
msgstr "Sut fedrwch chi gefnogi cod agored"

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:85
msgid "Contribute to a project"
msgstr "Cyfrannu at broject"

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:89
msgid ""
"Contribute to an existing open source project. Become a <a href="
"\"%(contribute)s\">Mozillian!</a> Or use <a href=\"%(open_hatch)s"
"\">OpenHatch</a> to match your skillset to a project."
msgstr ""
"Cyfrannu at broject cod agored cyfredol. Dod yn <a href=\"%(contribute)s"
"\">Mozilliad!</a> Neu ddefnyddio <a href=\"%(open_hatch)s\">OpenHatch</a> i "
"gydweddu eich sgiliau i broject."

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:93
msgid "Create something new"
msgstr "Creu rhywbeth newydd"

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:97
msgid ""
"Not sure where to start? Try our <a href=\"%(toolkit)s\">Open Innovation "
"Toolkit</a>."
msgstr ""
"DDim yn siŵr lle i gychwyn? Defnyddiwch ein <a href=\"%(toolkit)s\">Open "
"Innovation Toolkit</a>."

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:101
msgid "How Mozilla is supporting open source"
msgstr "Sut mae Mozilla yn cefnogi cod agored"

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:105
msgid "Contributing to the ecosystem"
msgstr "Cyfranu ar yr ecosystem"

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:109
msgid ""
"Contributing directly to the open source ecosystem through our products, "
"build systems, and back end systems, and fostering community through the <a "
"href=\"%(mdn)s\">Mozilla Developer Network</a>."
msgstr ""
"Rydym yn cyfrannu yn uniongyrchol i'r ecosystem cod agored drwy ein "
"cynnyrch, systemau adeiladu, a systemau cefn a thrwy feithrin cymuned drwy'r "
"<a href=\"%(mdn)s\">Mozilla Developer Network</a>."

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:113
msgid "Offering support"
msgstr "Cynnig cefnogaeth"

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:117
msgid ""
"Establishing <a href=\"%(moss)s\">MOSS</a>, the Mozilla Open Source Support "
"program, to give back to the movement we were born from."
msgstr ""
"Sefydlu <a href=\"%(moss)s\">MOSS</a>, y rhaglen Mozilla Open Source "
"Support, er mwyn rhoi nôl i'r symudiad o le gawsom ein geni."

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:121
msgid "Copyright: Reforming laws for our digital reality"
msgstr "Hawlfraint: Diwygio deddfau ar gyfer ein realiti digidol"

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:125
msgid ""
"We should all be able to share, reuse and reinterpret the creativity that "
"inspires us on the Internet."
msgstr ""
"Dylwn ni gyd allu rhannu, ailddefnyddio ac ail ddehongli'r creadigrwydd sy'n "
"ein hysbrydoli ar y Rhyngrwyd."

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:129
msgid ""
"Intellectual Property (IP) rights were designed as a practical solution to "
"advance creativity in all its forms: arts, science, business, and "
"technology. In order for IP to continue sowing seeds for the future of the "
"Web, our laws need to support the speed and spirit of collaboration that "
"defines our digital world."
msgstr ""
"Cafodd hawliau Eiddo Deallusol (IP) eu creu fel ateb ymarferol i "
"greadigrwydd uwch ym mhob ffurf: y celfyddydau, y gwyddorau, busnes a "
"thechnoleg. Er mwyn i IP barhau i hau hadau ar gyfer dyfodol y We, mae angen "
"i'n deddfau gynnal y cyflymder a'r ysbryd cydweithredol sy'n diffinio ein "
"byd digidol."

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:133
msgid ""
"There are now an estimated 1 billion Creative Commons-licensed works online "
"that encourage reuse, including texts, photos, and music."
msgstr ""
"Amcangyfrifir bod yna 1 biliwn o ddarnau gwaith o dan drwydded Creative "
"Commons ar-lein, sy'n annog eu hail ddefnyddio, gan gynnwys testun, lluniau "
"a cherddoriaeth."

#: mozorg/internet-health/open-innovation.lang:137
msgid "Source: <a href=\"%(cc)s\">Creative Commons</a>, 2015"
msgstr "Ffynhonnell: <a href=\"%(cc)s\">Creative Commons</a>, 2015"

#. This is used as a decorative element in a callout box. Keep it short.
